(sorry, I can use poor english.)

[Prepare]
If not exist, regist your twitter client application.
https://dev.twitter.com/apps/new

[2nd]
Open SceneDemo.unity.

[3rd]
Input your [Consumer key] and [Consumer secret] on SysTwitter's property, and save.

[4th]
Run this scene.
Click [Get Request Token] button.
If open browser, certificate your twitter account information.

[5th]
If you get PIN code, input it on the left side of [Enter PIN] button.
Click [Enter PIN].

[6th]
If you get AccessToken and AccessTokenSecret successfully, (See Console Window)
input tweet text on the left side of [Post Tweet] button.
Click [Post Tweet].

>>>>> Were you able to tweet successfully? Have fun.
